select valor, tabla, llave, 0 as marca from (select  valor = case when valor='articulo' then (select isnull(persoart, 'articulo') from [[instancia]advabousu[empresa]].dbo.config) 
			 when valor='honorario'	then  (select isnull(persohono, 'honorario') from [[instancia]advabousu[empresa]].dbo.config) 
			 when valor='suplido' then (select isnull(persogast, 'suplido') from [[instancia]advabousu[empresa]].dbo.config)
			 when valor='provision' then (select isnull(persoprov, 'provision') from [[instancia]advabousu[empresa]].dbo.config)
			 when valor='varios' then (select isnull(persovari, 'varios') from [[instancia]advabousu[empresa]].dbo.config)
			 when valor = 'provision recibida' then (select isnull(persoprov, 'provision') from  [[instancia]advabousu[empresa]].dbo.config) + ' RECIBIDA'
			 when valor = 'provision solicitada' then (select isnull(persoprov, 'provision') from  [[instancia]advabousu[empresa]].dbo.config) + ' SOLICITADA'
			 else upper(valor) end, tabla, llave

from [[instancia]advabocom].dbo.gestorvalores
WHERE tabla in ('cuentas')
AND llave = 'tipo'
and (valor not like 'kit' or (select bverkits from [[instancia]advabousu[empresa]].dbo.config) = 1)
and (valor not in ((select isnull(persoprov, 'provision') from  [[instancia]advabousu[empresa]].dbo.config) + ' SOLICITADA', (select isnull(persoprov, 'provision') from  [[instancia]advabousu[empresa]].dbo.config) + ' RECIBIDA') or (select count(id) from [[instancia]advabousu[empresa]].dbo.configvisualizacion where nombre='vertiposprov' and valor=1)=1)
and (valor not like (select isnull(persoprov, 'provision') from [[instancia]advabousu[empresa]].dbo.config)  or (select count(id) from [[instancia]advabousu[empresa]].dbo.configvisualizacion where nombre='vertiposprov' and valor=1)=0)
and (valor not like 'ANTICIPO' or (select count(id) from [[instancia]advabousu[empresa]].dbo.configvisualizacion where nombre='bveranticipo' and valor=1)=1)
UNION
select isnull(nullif(valor, ''), REPLACE(etiqueta, 'CuePrevi', 'PREVIAS ')) as valor, 'previas' as tabla, 'tipo' as llave from [[instancia]advabocom].dbo.etiquetasini where seccion like 'FormExpCue' 
	and 
	(
		(etiqueta = 'CuePrevi' and exists (select bverprevias from config WHERE bverprevias = 1))
		or (etiqueta = 'CuePrevi1' and exists (select bverprevias1 from config WHERE bverprevias1 = 1))
		or (etiqueta = 'CuePrevi2' and exists (select bverprevias2 from config WHERE bverprevias2 = 1))
		or (etiqueta = 'CuePrevi3' and exists (select bverprevias3 from config WHERE bverprevias3 = 1))
		or (etiqueta = 'CuePrevi4' and exists (SELECT 1 FROM [[instancia]advabousu[empresa]].dbo.ConfigVisualizacion WHERE nombre = 'bVerCalculoIntereses' AND valor = 1))
	)
) as valores
